    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know it sounds bad but i dont really want to go to the hospital if i dont have to. it's so expensive here and i'm pretty sure it's just the heat since i was outside for like 4 hours. if i just drink a bunch of electrolytes and sleep it off, i'll be fine by morning right? like, there's no way it's a stroke or anything, i just feel lightheaded.",
